A simple system to build a TUI (based on urwid) by plugins.

$ sudo yum install python python-urwind
$ cd src
$ ./app

Features
--------
- Clean separation between UI and data
- Pluggable
- UI
  - Resizable UI
  - Mouse support
  - Event based
- Model
  - With validation support


Sources
-------
http://excess.org/urwid/
